e performance issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"region_pending increased by 0.1963.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Maximum response time (rrt_max) increased significantly (3852.0 to 4524.0), indicating potential service performance degradation.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased by 0.1605.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Maximum response time (rrt_max) increased (2473.0 to 4038.0), indicating potential service performance issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased by 0.4807.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
